Modelo Banco de Dados

Bancos

  - User // Usuarios
  - Category // Categorias
  - Subcategory // Subcategorias
  - Process // Processos
  - Step // Etapas
  - Task // Tarefas
  - Comment // Comentarios
  - Department // Diretorias
  - Tag // Etiquetas
  
Especificações

  - User
    > Name - string
    > E-mail - string(usar regex)
    > Admin - boolean
    > Password - string
    > Photo - carrierwave com magick
    < has one Department
    
  - Category
    > Name - string
    > Description - text
    < has one Department
    < has many Subcategories
    < has many Processes
    
  - Subcategory
    > Name - string
    > Description - text
    < belongs to Categories
    < has many Processes
  
  - Process
    > Name - string
    > Description - text
    > Author - int (id do user)
    < belongs to Subcategory ?
    < belongs to Category
    < has many Comments
    
  - Step / Etapa
    > Name - string
    > Description - text
    < belongs to Column
    < belongs to Process
    < has many Tags
    < has many Comments

  - Column
    > Name - string
    < belongs to Department
    < belongs to Process
    
  - Comment
    > Text - text
    > Date - date
    < belongs to User
    
  - Department
    > Name - string
    > Director - user_id
    < has many Users
    < has many Tasks
    
  - Tag
    > Name - string (talvez, apenas pra identificar)
    > Color - string
    < belongs to Task